tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE dashboard_data ( 
  id UUID PRIMARY KEY, 
  name STRING, 
  value INT 
)

CREATE TABLE Visualization (
    vis_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    chart_type VARCHAR(50), 
    data_source_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (data_source_id) REFERENCES Dataset(id),
    dashboard_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (dashboard_id) REFERENCES Dashboard(dashboard_id)
);

CREATE TABLE dashboard_datasets (
  id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  dataset_name STRING,
  dataset_description STRING,
  created_at TIMESTAMP,
  last_updated_at TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE visualization_tools (
  tool_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  tool_name STRING,
  tool_description STRING,
  supported_features ARRAY<STRING>,
  release_date TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE user_activities (
  activity_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id UUID,
  activity_type STRING,
  activity_timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE dashboard_users (
  user_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  first_name STRING,
  last_name STRING,
  email STRING,
  registered_at TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE data_sources (
  source_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  source_name STRING,
  source_type STRING,
  connection_string STRING,
  added_at TIMESTAMP
)
